This paper is about a deep reinforcement learning algorithm, specifically Soft Actor-Critic (SAC), which is commonly studied in the machine learning subfield of reinforcement learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses off-policy sampling techniques and prioritized experience replay, which are relevant to subfields such as Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the algorithm on continuous-action Mujoco tasks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) research.
